sequenceDiagram
    actor Guard as Guard
    actor Admin as Admin
    participant UI as JavaFX Screens
    participant API as Spring Boot API
    participant Service as DeviceService
    participant DAO as StudentDAO / DeviceDAO
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Audit as AuditLogDAO

    Guard->>UI: Enter pending student/device details
    UI->>API: POST /devices pending registration
    API->>Service: submit pending device
    Service->>Service: validate student, serial, type, purpose
    Service->>DAO: insert/link student and insert pending device
    DAO->>DB: INSERT students if needed; INSERT devices registration_status=pending
    Service->>Audit: fn_write_audit_log DEVICE_REGISTERED
    API-->>UI: Pending device saved

    Admin->>UI: Open pending approval
    UI->>API: GET /devices pending queue
    API->>Service: load pending devices
    Service->>DAO: query v_pending_devices
    DAO->>DB: SELECT v_pending_devices
    DB-->>DAO: Pending rows
    API-->>UI: Pending list

    Admin->>UI: Approve or reject
    UI->>API: PUT /devices/{device_id}
    API->>Service: decide pending device
    Service->>DAO: persist registration_status and reviewer fields
    DAO->>DB: Device decision write
    Service->>Audit: fn_write_audit_log DEVICE_APPROVED or DEVICE_REJECTED
